ault\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p align=\"justify\">The partnership between home and school is absolutely vital. Colegio Gran Breta\u00f1a operates an \u201copen door\u201d policy and aims to work closely with parents while their child is at our school. Regular communication with parents is an important feature of school life. CGB Parents are always welcome to come into school.<\/p><p align=\"justify\">However, parents must not enter the classroom while lessons are in progress, except by invitation of the teacher. Formal parent-teacher consultations are held during the school year, according to the school calendar. Additionally, parents can ask at any time for an appointment with their child\u2019s teachers or the Director by directly contacting the person, by making an appointment through the office or through Phidias, the school\u2019s communication system.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-75c36f2 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-content-middle elementor-section-height-min-height elementor-section-items-stretch elementor-section-height-default ae-bg-gallery-type-default\" data-id=\"75c36f2\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;,&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-a6a4631 animated-fast ae-bg-gallery-type-default elementor-invisible\" data-id=\"a6a4631\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;,&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;slideInRight&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5fbab2c elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"5fbab2c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7386671 uael-dual-heading-align-left elementor-widget elementor-widget-uael-dual-color-heading\" data-id=\"7386671\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"uael-dual-color-heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"uael-module-content uael-dual-color-heading uael-heading-stack-none\">\n\t\t\t<h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"uael-before-heading\"><span class=\"elementor-inline-editing uael-dual-heading-text uael-first-text\" data-elementor-setting-key=\"before_heading_text\" data-elementor-inline-editing-toolbar=\"basic\">PARENT COUNCIL<\/span><\/span><span class=\"uael-adv-heading-stack\"><span class=\"elementor-inline-editing uael-dual-heading-text uael-highlight-text\" data-elementor-setting-key=\"second_heading_text\" data-elementor-inline-editing-toolbar=\"basic\">PURPOSE<\/span><\/span>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/h2>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2442341 parrafo-pagina-interna elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2442341\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The Parent Council is a group of parents with currently enrolled students aimed at continuing parent participation in the educational process and raising the quality of service results.<\/p><p>At least one main member and one substitute will be elected for each of the grades from Nursery to year 13, in accordance with the provisions of the PEI institutional educational project, to form this Council.<\/p><p>The Council meets several times a year with the aim of discussing All its responsibilities and mainly general situations presented by the parents which require a solution or proposal from the school.<\/p><p>Find more on Phidias \/ Community \/ Global Files<\/p><div>\u00a0<\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-76eaf84 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"76eaf84\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-b4a8746 animated-fast ae-bg-gallery-type-default elementor-invisible\" data-id=\"b4a8746\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;slideInLeft&quot;,&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9c2fcab elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"9c2fcab\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_ae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-elemen